<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section class="py-5 bg-light-custom">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="text-center text-muted mb-5">Find answers to common questions about our AI-powered tools</p>

        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-header" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq1">
                        How does the AI resume builder work?
                    </div>
                    <div id="faq1" class="collapse show faq-body">
                        <p>Our AI analyzes thousands of successful resumes in your field to provide personalized suggestions. It evaluates your input, suggests powerful action verbs, optimizes bullet points, and ensures your resume contains the right keywords for Applicant Tracking Systems. The more information you provide, the better the AI can tailor its recommendations to your specific situation.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-header collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq2">
                        Can the AI write my entire resume for me?
                    </div>
                    <div id="faq2" class="collapse faq-body">
                        <p>Our AI can generate complete resume sections based on the information you provide about your work history and skills. However, we recommend reviewing and personalizing the AI's suggestions to ensure they accurately represent your unique experience. The AI serves as a powerful assistant, but you remain in complete control of the final content.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-header collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq3">
                        How does the AI portfolio builder select my best work?
                    </div>
                    <div id="faq3" class="collapse faq-body">
                        <p>Our AI evaluates your projects based on several factors including complexity, relevance to your target jobs, visual appeal (for creative fields), and the skills demonstrated. It then suggests which projects to highlight and even recommends the optimal order to present them for maximum impact.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-header collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq4">
                        Is my data used to train the AI models?
                    </div>
                    <div id="faq4" class="collapse faq-body">
                        <p>We prioritize your privacy. Your personal data is never used to train our AI models without your explicit consent. All information you provide is encrypted and stored securely. You maintain full ownership of your resume and portfolio content at all times.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-header collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq5">
                        Can the AI help me tailor my resume for specific jobs?
                    </div>
                    <div id="faq5" class="collapse faq-body">
                        <p>Yes! Our AI can analyze job descriptions and suggest modifications to better align your resume with specific positions. Premium members can paste job descriptions to get tailored keyword suggestions and content recommendations that match what employers are looking for.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

